name: Franny
description:
100% wool; super soft without any itch! Super cozy, with all the warmth you desire and none of the overheating. This super slouchy, handmade hat is knit "sideways" making it look more slouchy and well-loved over time, with a false rib keeping it fitting snugly around your head, keeping your ears warm all winter long. Great for both boys and girls, Franny's super slouchy style is the perfect accent to any outfit.

100% handmade, with love & squalor.
